IF YOU HAVEN’T ALREADY:

pkg <- c("tidyverse", "gapminder")
install.packages(pkg)
library(magrittr)
library(dplyr)
library(ggplot2)
library(gapminder)

While everyone is getting ready:

  • play around with the gapminder dataset

library(dplyr)
